data.description: Welcome to 452 Pershing St, Box Elder, SD, located in a spacious, established neighborhood close to Douglas Schools and Ellsworth AFB! This well loved and maintained home has 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 2 car garage and a large fenced yard. A comfortable open concept home with an efficient layout, great natural light, and a warm energy ideal for relaxing and entertaining inside and out. Upstairs the master bedroom suite has a private bathroom, walk-in closet, dual sinks, trayed ceiling and a second bedroom. Large front entry way with a coat closet. Downstairs you have a 24’ x 15’ family room, two large bedrooms, and a full bathroom. Large private fully fenced backyard, with play set, hot tub, firepit, shed and no neighbors behind. OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY February 03, 2:00 to 4:00 PM.  Please see virtual tour at https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=gE6RFPPwtC1&mls=1
